      "content": "thanks for this. the draft looks a lot better than what i had. i like how you mentioned the kubernetes stuff specifically. could you maybe add one more paragraph? i want to emphasize that it wasn't a lack of skill on their part, just a matter of very specific niche alignment for our current team. something that makes it clear they are still a top-tier engineer.",
